output.analysis:
Let's analyze this post according to our criteria:
1. Has CMF: Yes - CMF 11240017 is present, indicating this is electoral content.
2. Refers to candidate: Yes - Mentions Marcel Ciolacu explicitly, who is a presidential candidate (Position 3).
3. Addresses wide population: Yes - This is a paid post with significant reach (45,000-50,000 impressions) on Facebook and Instagram.
4. Electoral objective: Mixed - While primarily focused on parliamentary elections (which are allowed), it also promotes Marcel Ciolacu's "country projects" and uses PSD's presidential campaign slogan "#CaleaSigurăPentruRomânia".
5. Journalism: No - This is clearly a campaign message, not journalistic content.
6. Personal opinion: No - This is an official party communication from PSD Maramures.
Key concerns: - While mainly about parliamentary elections (which would be allowed), it promotes Marcel Ciolacu's initiatives - Uses presidential campaign messaging ("#CaleaSigurăPentruRomânia") - Has significant reach through paid promotion - Includes CMF number confirming its propaganda nature

conclusion.electoral-propaganda-analysis: This post presents a complex case as it mixes parliamentary campaign (allowed) with presidential messaging (not allowed after campaign end). While primarily discussing local meetings and parliamentary candidates, it promotes Marcel Ciolacu's projects and uses presidential campaign slogans. The presence of CMF number and paid promotion confirms its propaganda nature.
conclusion.message-for-police: PSD Maramures, pentru incalcarea articolului 55 t) din Legea 370/2004, prin continuarea propagandei electorale pentru candidatul prezidential Marcel Ciolacu dupa incheierea perioadei de campanie, prin postarea cu ID 1120036146358587 promovata pe Facebook si Instagram dupa ora 18:00 pe 23.11.2024. Postarea promoveaza "proiectele de țară propuse de Marcel Ciolacu" si foloseste sloganul campaniei prezidentiale "#CaleaSigurăPentruRomânia", avand un efect electoral direct prin promovarea imaginii si proiectelor candidatului la presedintie. Postarea este marcata cu cod CMF 11240017, confirmand natura sa de propaganda electorala, si a fost promovata platit catre un public larg de 45.000-50.000 persoane.
